name: Dark Strike A.T.F. - Advanced Tactical Fighter
name_original: Dark Strike A.T.F. - Advanced Tactical Fighter
description:
Dark Strike A.T.F. - Advanced Tactical Fighter is an arcade game developed by Prisim Games. It was originally released in 1995. It was published by Prisim Games.
Dark Strike A.T.F. - Advanced Tactical Fighter is available on PC.
